				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Regen hitting Monks?????<a name="35545"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 20 04 8:19 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey folks, Wiladancer here with a quick question:
<br />

<br />
If a Monk is pulling (now please save your comments about how much better bards are at pulling, I know, I know) and I am singing Wind of Marr (lvl 62) for my group. Should he come within range of the song and Feign Death, would the pulsing of regen draw aggro to me or negate his FD? I am curious as I have witnessed both. It may be that range is the true factor here, but in semi-tight quarters, I believe it transfers the aggro and negates the FD. 
<br />

<br />
Your insight is greatly appreciated.
<br />

<br />
Wiladancer Eversing 
<br />
&quot;Can I get KEI too?&quot;</span></td>
