				<td colspan="2"><span>This is correct.  Group or AOE heals affecting the monk will add you to any mobs the monk has agroed and is pulling before he FDs.  When the monk is FD and is lying on the ground, those songs will not generate agro.  Hitting him once he stands up may add you to the agro list as well if the monk did not achieve a complete mem wipe and is within reagro range of the mobs.</span></td>
