				<td colspan="2"><span>After being FD for two minutes, you get a message similar to &quot;Your enemies have forgotten you!&quot; and your aggro is wiped. I'm positive it works this way for the spell versions of FD, at least. It's a recent change.
<br />

<br />
Here's how to get chain aggro off your monk friends:
<br />
-Monk leaves on the pull, you're probably playing Marr at this point during downtime. When your song hits here, it's obviously not a problem
<br />
-Your song hits the monk as he runs back w/ aggro'd mobs
<br />
-Monk FD's to split mobs
<br />
-You get trained by anything that aggroed the monk (and anything those mobs chain aggro onto you).</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
